## CORS

Configure CORS in `main.py` only. Never configure it inside a router.

```python
from fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware

app.add_middleware(
    CORSMiddleware,
    allow_origins=["http://localhost:3000"],  # add Vercel URL in production
    allow_credentials=True,
    allow_methods=["*"],
    allow_headers=["*"],
)
```